~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Ranks~RS    : POD Shaman                              ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Synopsis~RS : POD Shaman is an admin rank.  Shaman have access to
              almost all the commands available.  The user at this level is
              responsible for maintenance of POD, promotions, and most
              importantly a working knowledge of the pod as a whole.
              Shaman are responsible for making judgment calls on new
              users, interacting with Elders and Leaders to help achieve
              balance between all ranks of POD.  In the absence of a POD
              Leader, the Shaman's word is the final word. 

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   User has a total of 120 commands.
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
